name: DS-181-3
Lore: 'Flies Saber 3 in fighting 181st. Studied under Baron Fel at the Prefsbelt Imperial Academy; now flies as his wing. Nicknamed ''Fel''s Wrath''. Watches the Baron''s back.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Saber 3, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Opponent may not ''react'' to same system or sector.',
